data.title: 50 U.S. State Songs
data.meta_description: State songs list for each of the 50 states of the US. Select the song to find out the song and even hear the state song!
data.text:
There are 49 official state songs that have been voted in by each state’s local government as the official song. New Jersey is the only state in the US without an official state song, but they do have a popular one that has been designated “the unofficial state song of New Jersey”.

There are a few states that actually have multiple songs too. The style of the song varies from state to state. Some sound like catchy anthems and some are just songs that celebrate the state.
